f a higher excited state is\npresented where the Bohmian approximation does not perform so well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Nov 2020 18:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2022 15:23:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-13"}
