stem\nillustrates is a state in which an electron cyclotron maser emission can be\nsustained in a planet's magnetic polar regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2020 11:05:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Nov 2020 13:11:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-04"}
